# NERD Comment

Comments current line or visual mode selection
,cc

Toggles on/off comment
,c<space>

Comments using only one set of multipart delimiters
,cm

Comments out the selected lines “sexily”
,cs

Commented line(s) are yanked
,cy

Comments the current line from the cursor to the end of line
,c$

Comment to the end of line and goes into insert mode
,cA

Comment to the start of line and goes into insert mode between
them.
,cI

Switches to the alternative set of delimiters
,ca

Same as |NERDComComment| except that the delimiters are aligned down the
left side (,cl), the right side (,cr) or both sides
,cl OR ,cr OR ,cb
(,cb)
,cl
,cr
,cb

Uncomments any commented lines in the block (only one level if nested)
,cu

